messageBody:
On 10/17/06, dulani_udayangani <dulani_udayangani@...> wrote:
> how to import junit libraries in to TestCase .

Did I understand you correctly that you're looking for this statement?

import junit.framework.TestCase;

If it's not that, then you'll have to elaborate because at least I
don't have the vaguest idea of what you mean by "importing junit
libraries into TestCase"?

Lasse
